descp2: The axes along which to share learnable parameters for the activation function. For example, if the incoming feature maps are from a 2D convolution with output shape `(batch, height, width, channels)`, and you wish to share parameters across space so that each filter only has one set of parameters, set `shared_axes=[1, 2]`.

The axes along which to share learnable parameters for the activation function. For example, if the incoming feature maps are from a 2D convolution with output shape `(batch, height, width, channels)`, and you wish to share parameters across space so that each filter only has one set of parameters, set `shared_axes=[1, 2]`.
